<h1><strong>Welcome to WedWeb!!</strong></h1>

<em><h2>We are your personal all-in-one wedding planner!</h2></em>

<h4>Our features include: </h4>
<ul>
  <li>Create your wedding. Add your partner's email so they can see all the features.</li>
  <li>Invite your guests with our easy-to-use emailer. They will recieve a link and key to your wedding's website. Here they can create a profile to see your registry, all your events, chose from your menu and specify their dietary preferences making origanizing guest charts a breeze!</li>
  <li>Post a wedding social page for your loved ones to see, share, and comment on.</li>
  <li>Link and share your gift registry --- so you don't end up with four of the same toasters!</li>
  <li>Create events like Ceremony, Reception, Engagement Party etc on one page, so your guests arrive at the right place at the right time.</li>
  <li>Guests can also create a profile, enter in their information, and see maps for their routes to get to your events</li>
  <li>Create a seating chart using your guest list and print off seating and plate choices for all your vendores</li>
</ul>

